        %h2.sr-only About The Project
        :kramdown
          The creators of [Postsnap][ps], a popular iPhone app for sending personalised cards, approached us with a similar idea for flowers.

          They wanted to start completely fresh, utilising our expertise in modern #{define('iOS')} development to create a beautiful app for customising and buying bouquets.

          We jumped at the chance! [Postabloom][pb] is now available on the UK App Store for download.

