        %h2
          = fa_icon("truck")
          Stock Control and Delivery

        :kramdown
          While the customer app is clean and simple, there is a lot more to Postabloom behind-the-scenes. We worked closely with the team to build a robust, fully-fledged product management system that lets them keep up with orders even on Valentines day.

          Our web-driven back-end receives orders from the app, automatically generating barcodes and PDF templates for Postabloom's various fulfilment companies.

          On the factory floor, printing a postage label is as simple as scanning a barcode.

