          The Latest Mobile Technology
        :kramdown
          With an in-house developer and an app already in the Store, Postsnap knew what goes in to building a good iPhone app. The team didn't just want to expand on what they had though, they wanted Postabloom to be a best-in-class app for shopping on #{define('iOS')}.

          To make sure the app lasted for years to come, we built it in [Swift][], Apple's new language designed for faster, more stable apps. The interface is also scalable to cover the increasing variety of devices Apple offers.

          We look forward to bringing Postabloom to the iPad soon!


